{"tid":289747,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【主權移交中國廿周年前夕　民族黨辦晚會冀港人重拾自信","createTime":"2017-06-19T09:05:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-25T04:11:37.000Z","uid":111279,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c9ed417c36febff357f5e902a840ad79e34d898d","tid":289747,"uid":111279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T09:05:53.000Z","msg":"【主權移交中國廿周年前夕　民族黨辦晚會冀港人重拾自信「諗返起我哋曾經幾咁風光」】<br />\n<br />\n香港民族黨召集人陳浩天今日（十九日）表示，將於本月三十日晚在尖沙咀鐘樓舉行和平晚會，悼念香港淪陷二十年，讓香港人緬懷主權移交前的光輝歲月，重拾香港人的自信，「諗返起當年我哋幾咁風光、我地係幾咁巴閉，我地香港有咁既成就，其實同中國完全無關」。他說，當年除了是靠英國人的制度，最重要的是香港人的奮鬥、拼博精神和創造力，但這廿年中國不斷貶低香港的自信，不斷給香港人洗腦要靠中國，所以希望藉著晚會讓重拾香港人的自信。他又指，希望這次晚會可以團結支持港獨和本土派的市民。<br />\n<br />\n[url]網址[/url]<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=1936922776524194&amp;id=1487928594756950\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D1936922776524194%26id%3D1487928594756950&d=lDAs88%2FZOpgUNEcUdrqcvv6YfqAiA4jm3R2Vm1010vU%3D&h=8665684a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=1936922776524194&amp;id=1487928594756950</a>"},{"pid":"1c2f2248a5d30b88d352aa9a6215a8f897984b8e","tid":289747,"uid":111279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T09:06:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c4ecd94546f4785c5896c43361daa51bab64c03","tid":289747,"uid":49784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T03:46:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/42.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7ff4d2964110d9bd4b47f291ff9159c09d495d0","tid":289747,"uid":64409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T04:11:37.000Z","msg":"HK no.1<im